{"TopicId":140796,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Slash key among others unresponsive","CreatedByName":"Elfman","CreatedById":164958,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-30T03:57:47Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Elfman","CreatedById":164958,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-30T03:57:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy specs : - Japanese Mac laptop keyboard (no numpad) with latest version of OS X, and most recent KSP build 1.1.2...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlthough my / _ : ] [ @ \u00A5\u00A0keys work fine outside of KSP\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthey become\u00A0unresponsive during KSP gameplay\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:huh:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_undecided.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:huh:\u0022\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve found a\u00A0temporary solution of reassign them to secondary input keys in the settings menu but I\u0027m seeking a more permanent solution as some mods use these same keys to activate their mods, and I don\u0027t think it\u0027s possible to reassign mod activation keys.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny ideas?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-30T09:35:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/164958-elfman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022164958\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/164958-elfman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Elfman\u003C/a\u003E, have you tried setting a US English keyboard layout?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf that is successful you could start KSP via a script that sets the keyboard \u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Environment_variable\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Eenvironment variable\u003C/a\u003E to US English for you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Elfman","CreatedById":164958,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-04T12:27:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you so much \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/16426-sal_vager/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002216426\u0022 href=\u0022%7B___base_url___%7D/index.php?/profile/16426-sal_vager/\u0022 rel=\u0022external\u0022\u003E@sal_vager\u003C/a\u003E,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI didn\u0027t imagine a game as\u00A0internationally popular as KSP\u00A0would required a change in keyboard language \u0026amp; nationality.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut hey...\u00A0it\u0027s working great...an\u00A0easier\u00A0fix than reassigning\u00A0all the keys manually. Thanks again\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-06-04T12:29:01Z\u0022 title=\u002206/04/2016 12:29  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJune 4, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Elfman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}